dct_title_s: [Kharitat al-Iraq]: shu'bata as-Suwayrah wa al-Mahmudiyah = Sections of Suwaira and Mahmudia
dct_description_sm: Iraq. Mudiriyat ar-Rayy al-Ammah Shu'bat al-Misaha. Iraq. General Directorate of Irrigation. Survey Division. Alternate title: Liwa'ay Baghdad wa al-Kut: Qada'ay as-Suwayrah wa al-Mahmudiya: Shu'bata as-Suwayrah wa al-Mahmudiya. = Provinces of Baghdad and al-Kut: districts of Suwaira and Mahmudiya: sections of Suwaira and Mahmudia. Relief shown by hachures and form lines. Triangulation points are shown. Surveyed: 1929-30. Tribal lands and ownership sare hown.
